snippet.title: Rate My Takeaway
snippet.description:
Join Danny on his search to find the best/worst takeaways. 

Rate My Takeaway is your video guide to finding the best places to eat from local business in your area. After months of hearing from the community, we sent Danny to try & test some of the highly recommended places that you've all been telling us about for the last 3 years.

What first started as a small Facebook Group has now become your way of skipping the menus and to find out what's new in your area.

You can contact us anytime by emailing ratetakeaway@outlook.com
